  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AcceptRejectGUI
    The Accept/Reject Interface JPanel Allows the Program Chair make the accept/reject decision for a paper in the CMS.
    AssignReviewerGUI
    The Assign Reviewer Interface JPanel Allows the user to assign a reviewer(s) to a paper in the CMS.
    AssignSubPCGUI
    The Assign Sub-Program Chair Interface JPanel Allows the Program Chair to assign a Sub-Program Chair to a paper in the CMS.
    ConferenceGUI
    The View Conference Panel Allows the user to see an overview of conference and view the attached paper objects
    EditSubmissionGUI
    The Edit Submission Interface JPanel Allows the user to edit a submitted paper in the CMS.
    GUIEnum
    The enumeration class that holds the enums for: GUI state, paper status that's viewable for administrative purposes, paper status that's viewable for author's purposes, and the relationship a user logged in has with a paper.
    HomeGUI
    The Main User Interface JPanel Allows the user to create new conferences, see conferences they're associated with, and see all other upcoming conferences.
    LoginGUI
    The Login user interface JPanel
    MainFrame
    The Main Frame to run the CMS software in.
    MakeRecommendationGUI
    The Make Recommendation Interface JPanel Allows the user to make a recommendation for a paper in the CMS.
    ManagementPanel
    The Management JPanel used within the ManagePaperGUI to display current administrative fields.
    ManagePaperGUI
    The Manage Paper User Interface JPanel Allows the user to create access all the information relevant to a conference and a paper in relation to their permissions associated with that paper.
    NewConferenceGUI
    The New Conference Interface JPanel Allows the user to create a new conference in the CMS.
    PaperFrame  
    RecommendPanel
    The RecommendPanel JPanel creates a panel containing recommendations already submitted.
    RegisterGUI
    The RegisterGUI JPanel.
    ReviewPanel
    The Review Panel creates a sub-panel of Reviews submitted to be displayed in the ManagePaperGUI
    SubmitPaperGUI
    The Submit Paper Interface JPanel Allows the user to submit a paper in the CMS.
    SubmitReviewGUI
    The Submit Review Interface JPanel Allows the user to submit a review relevant to a paper in the CMS.
